Ivory Coast Violence Flares in Abidjan, Leaving at Least One Person Dead

-- B y   O l i v i e r   M o n n i e r   a n d   P a u l i n e   B a x
-- 
2011-02-21T13:25:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/ivory-coast-violence-flares-in-abidjan-leaving-at-least-one-person-dead.html
At least one person was killed after
shootings in the Treichville neighborhood of Abidjan,  Ivory
Coast ’s commercial capital, according to a resident.  “The security forces are here and they have been shooting
around, everybody is scared,” Chantal Guehennot said by phone.  Gunfire was also reported in Koumassi, a neighborhood in
the south of Abidjan, where protesters were demonstrating, said
Didier Houldesso, a member of the youth wing of the opposition
Parti Democratique de Cote d’Ivoire by phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
